{"tid":254142,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解柯鎮惡可以咁長命？","createTime":"2017-05-23T03:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T02:05:47.000Z","uid":14703,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"891d55f6321ceadd02ebe73250c3fe88ee693d7c","tid":254142,"uid":14703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"佢出場個陣原版四十幾<br />\n新修係三十幾<br />\n當你三十五喇<br />\n<br />\n然後搵郭靖加埋教佢武功過左十八年<br />\n<br />\n射鵰故事大約一兩年左右<br />\n<br />\n之後又過左十幾年去到神鵰，當你十五年喇，<br />\n<br />\n楊過小龍女一別十六年之後<br />\n<br />\n佢仲可以好精神咁同楊過講幾十年前發生既事<br />\n無老人痴呆仲咁健康真係好犀利<br />\n計一計佢都應該八十幾九十<br />\n<br />\n仲有如果佢一出場得三十五，點解成個頭都白哂<br />\n又要拎拐杖<br />\n一個阿伯咁既態維持左五十幾年...好恐怖"},{"pid":"770f2a42ca1e0769b8438e0cbb62197b4759eeb3","tid":254142,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"因為係小說"},{"pid":"b586087a2169c069adcd1d714fb876044f4421a1","tid":254142,"uid":51436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c29b618a854bb664d026f3153911f6e772f4089","tid":254142,"uid":14703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為係小說</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小說都要什個原因佢架wo<br />\n你話佢有咩神功咁長命<br />\n或者郭靖養佢師父養到肥肥白白就話姐<br />\n但係佢後生已經成個阿伯咁<br />\n點睇都唔似長命百歲wo"},{"pid":"346e507b8c0a84e0b907b5638ca6d03490682ba0","tid":254142,"uid":67332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為係小說</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小說都要什個原因佢架wo<br />\n你話佢有咩神功咁長命<br />\n或者郭靖養佢師父養到肥肥白白就話姐<br />\n但係佢後生已經成個阿伯咁<br />\n點睇都唔似長命百歲wo</blockquote><br />\n佢好似中過九陰百骨爪，中完之後急速老化"},{"pid":"3549800de37e4090faefe6700991ab8f9a3d43b6","tid":254142,"uid":14703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為係小說</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小說都要什個原因佢架wo<br />\n你話佢有咩神功咁長命<br />\n或者郭靖養佢師父養到肥肥白白就話姐<br />\n但係佢後生已經成個阿伯咁<br />\n點睇都唔似長命百歲wo</blockquote><br />\n佢好似中過九陰百骨爪，中完之後急速老化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n九陰白骨爪好似一招喪命架wo..."},{"pid":"108821deb2c1350973a9b951769976432207d22a","tid":254142,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為係小說</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小說都要什個原因佢架wo<br />\n你話佢有咩神功咁長命<br />\n或者郭靖養佢師父養到肥肥白白就話姐<br />\n但係佢後生已經成個阿伯咁<br />\n點睇都唔似長命百歲wo</blockquote><br />\n後期係桃花島養生唔出奇"},{"pid":"4c07155ffce7257f8b9ae8464fdeb11c03f62228","tid":254142,"uid":62060,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終日無所事事指手劃腳，屌鳩郭靖楊過係廢青<br />\n攤手板攞綜援，住桃花島痴飲痴食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f21be58118bdf8c179ca8af43b964229813c66","tid":254142,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:06:09.000Z","msg":"呢個問題真係要問金老先生..."},{"pid":"a5213c24f460052b8a70d1d6f93d1ee6bfe5f7a3","tid":254142,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"因為係廢老"},{"pid":"d18f178b8632db1ad41dc98aee2b988d7c442e75","tid":254142,"uid":102703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"點解瑛姑可以一剎那黑髮變白髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72a2414a6194a60637a71afc0e72eda3673094b","tid":254142,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:18:08.000Z","msg":"周伯通先長命"},{"pid":"2c76d159fa79ab64387a75dff0200e70f1f500f8","tid":254142,"uid":93266,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解瑛姑可以一剎那黑髮變白髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用左美源髮彩..."},{"pid":"0dbb4e1e00a1ea38d866b180027de99a5b0e2dc2","tid":254142,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"最恐怖嘅係 你唔知佢出咗幾成力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044370e3205ef4a90bf31b26edac7805089a5f00","tid":254142,"uid":64990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"其實江南七怪咁撚屎，一早比人打死左啦，btw原著黃藥師好似有搞過童年既梅超風，有無巴打有印象？"},{"pid":"2553ed84878e4441b2ad486182a4ae03ec91f930","tid":254142,"uid":1802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為係小說</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小說都要什個原因佢架wo<br />\n你話佢有咩神功咁長命<br />\n或者郭靖養佢師父養到肥肥白白就話姐<br />\n但係佢後生已經成個阿伯咁<br />\n點睇都唔似長命百歲wo</blockquote><br />\n佢好似中過九陰百骨爪，中完之後急速老化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n九陰白骨爪好似一招喪命架wo...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果陣梅超風功力未成呀嗎<br />\n啱啱練左下卷冇耐，加上唔係中佢要害，淨係插瞎左。"},{"pid":"6ece97f5cbdd9bd52e563ff1e8a6b03b0fdab4d1","tid":254142,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"日日食桃花鳥補品"},{"pid":"f63f099aa8384618923f938cebbe465be613496a","tid":254142,"uid":14703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周伯通先長命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n周伯通係全真教既人<br />\n又練過九陰真經<br />\n長命d都唔出奇"},{"pid":"64e3e6384ffa89133b3c8e29b4d846b603f52d94","tid":254142,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"江南七怪個名好似好響，但成班都係垃圾黎，打又唔夠人打，教又唔識教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59143056117a1e066ddd330361b47892d046db7","tid":254142,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>江南七怪個名好似好響，但成班都係垃圾黎，打又唔夠人打，教又唔識教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個組合名七怪已經好清楚, 只係7個7頭,<br />\n冇人話好好打, 或者識教人"},{"pid":"f5cabdd83b6ae4bc6f7e1853d253ccda9083834b","tid":254142,"uid":14703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>江南七怪個名好似好響，但成班都係垃圾黎，打又唔夠人打，教又唔識教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹想討論下點解柯鎮惡咁長命<br />\n佢地勁唔勁唔重要<br />\n<br />\n但係你話佢地唔識教我就唔認同<br />\n最起碼佢教到郭靖咩叫「俠」<br />\n係佢地培養出郭靖既俠義精神<br />\n（當然都同蒙古人既成長環境同佢老豆既經歷有些少影響）<br />\n雖然佢地好廢，<br />\n但係佢地為左一個承諾，就用左十八年走去蒙古教個三唔識七既細路。<br />\n<br />\n相反你丘處機堂堂全真七子同郭楊二人叫做一場相識<br />\n教楊康咁多年教到咁既死款先叫唔識教<br />\n（顯然佢都無心教）"},{"pid":"cf372b88f298440f2c36c0a215d3d1a5311bd980","tid":254142,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"呀大師父好撚傳統 好封建 一就係一 二就係二 唔識變通<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19be3314c225c84f4b30c8d414f2c65afb02609b","tid":254142,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實江南七怪咁撚屎，一早比人打死左啦，btw原著黃藥師好似有搞過童年既梅超風，有無巴打有印象？</blockquote><br />\n好似話鐘意過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4c41ad6c1894b0e92b27654de9885ca84ea005","tid":254142,"uid":14703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀大師父好撚傳統 好封建 一就係一 二就係二 唔識變通<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=